   "source": [
    "# 🚗 Smart Parking YOLO Model Training & Testing\n",
    "\n",
    "## Overview\n",
    "This notebook trains YOLO models for:\n",
    "1. **Vehicle Detection** - Detect vehicle types (car, bus, motorcycle, etc.)\n",
    "2. **License Plate Detection** - Detect Indian number plates\n",
    "\n",
    "## Datasets\n",
    "- **Vehicle Detection**: 6 classes (bus, car, motorcycle, pickup-truck, semi-trailer, van)\n",
    "- **Number Plate Detection**: 1 class (number_plate)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Testing Conditions\n",
    "- Various lighting conditions\n",
    "- Different angles and distances\n",
    "- Multiple vehicle scenarios\n",
    "- Real-time performance validation"
   ]
  },
  {
